data.description: This property sits in Simmons Shores division with a community pool and boat ramp.  If you're looking for a weekend getaway or permanant lake living, this is the place for you.  Four bedrooms for larger families or lake visitors. Highport Marina is a short drive away for all the holiday and weekend festivities. Tanglewood resort and golf is just a few minutes away as well.  Launch the boat and take a few minute cruise over to Grandpappy Point for Sunday brunch on the lake.  Location, location, location.  You are in the middle of it all.  Lake Texoma is home to one of the few striper habitats in Oklahoma or Texas and it is amazing for the angler in the family. The private back yard at the house will be great for entertainment after your day at the lake.
